00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:08,910
You really don't want to join the match?

528
00:35:08,910 --> 00:35:11,169
Is this your decision?

529
00:35:12,330 --> 00:35:14,728
Didn't you promise to never give up?

530
00:35:14,728 --> 00:35:17,109
You want to become a puppy?

