00:35:17,990 --> 00:35:19,390
You...

532
00:35:20,789 --> 00:35:22,489
I...

533
00:35:22,489 --> 00:35:25,050
I'm talking to you!

534
00:36:06,430 --> 00:36:09,830
Are you alright?

535
00:36:09,830 --> 00:36:14,449
I was thinking about the time I started archery for the past few days.

536
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:28,688
Here! Over the line.

537
00:36:28,688 --> 00:36:31,150
Parallel to it.

538
00:36:31,150 --> 00:36:33,889
Feet at shoulder width.

539
00:36:33,889 --> 00:36:35,870
Stand straight.

540
